snippet.title: Enotria: The Last Song - Official Trailer
snippet.description:
Check out the action-packed cinematic trailer for upcoming soulslike, Enotria: The Last Song.

Enotria: The Last Song has a planned release date of September 18, 2024 for PS5 (PlayStation 5) and PC (Steam and Epic Games Store). The demo is available to play now.

#IGN #Gaming #Enotria
